Yes I noticed 4 patterns
Wop... (circle)
Gaf.... (kind of like a star of five arms)
Buvik (pentagon)
Zetty (2 five-pointed stars one rotated) 
This stage was easy!
But the hardest part was the ends of some words.... It was terribly difficult some word endings "oe" "ow" "cow" "kcoe" it was hard to remember, there should be one form and not some different variations!
